flowchart TD
    Input[User Command] --> Scanner[Risk Pattern Scanner]
    Scanner -->|Safe| Execute[Execute Command]
    Scanner -->|Destructive| Warn[Display Warning]
    Warn --> Confirm{User Confirms?}
    Confirm -->|Yes| Execute
    Confirm -->|No| Cancel[Cancel]
    Execute --> Result{Exit Code}
    Result -->|Error| Recovery[Recovery Engine]
    Recovery --> Rules{Pattern Match?}
    Rules -->|Yes| InstantFix[Instant Fix Suggestion]
    Rules -->|No| LLM[LLM Diagnosis]
    Result -->|Success| History[SQLite History]
    Execute --> History
